title: The Night Lennon Died - Toronto Radio Scan - Dec 8, 1980
description:
In the background you hear some news, your ears perk up to be sure you heard right --  you heard right.  The feeling is heart-wrenching, you are confused/angry/sorrowful/numb - totally numb.

This Toronto-radio-scan recording was made within moments of hearing 'that' news -- in the late hours of December 8th, 1980, and on into the new day.

The Night Lennon Died - Toronto Radio Scan
December 8, 1980 late pm, into the new day.

64 Kbps, 22050 Hz, Stereo (11.0:1)
2 x 45 mins
